data.description: Maintained with pride of ownership. This 4/2.5 home is in great condition. In the heart of West Palm Beach and close to everything, with three easy entry points to the I-95 nearby.DO NOTHING FOR HURRICANES - 23 impact windows and doors installed 2018.  LED lighting throughout. Properly maintained AC Unit with UV light filter, new water heater. Smart controls for sprinklers, lights, and AC. Gated community with pools, playgrounds, tennis courts, basketball courts and events. Primary bedroom with upgraded suite bathroom and large walk-in closet. 4th bedroom is perfect for a home office. Manned guards, cameras, quiet, safe, gated community.
